root.npcDialog: Hi, are you ok?  I am your guide to this land. What do you want to know about?

nextDialogs.playerReply: Who are you?
nextDialogs.npcDialog: I am your guide to this land, any question?

nextDialogs.playerReply: I want to know about how to walk around here.
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Sure.  You can 'go north' or any of the north, east, west, south direction to move around the map

nextDialogs.playerReply: yeah, I know that, but where I can't go?.
nextDialogs.npcDialog: You will find it out yourself, there is a invisible air wall that stop everyone here from walking outside the world.

nextDialogs.playerReply: Oh, like walking south at here?.
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Yeah, you are smart dude.  You might also want to know that here is a dangerous place.

nextDialogs.playerReply: Don't you dare to scare me!.
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Hey, chill dude, if you don't trust me, you can try 'detect' once you walk to a new place

nextDialogs.playerReply: That is a cool!
nextDialogs.npcDialog: In that way, you can find out monster or any item in that coordinate

nextDialogs.playerReply: So I can 'attack' these monster?
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Of cause, if you are brave enough, you can gain xp and gold by defeating them.  But if you lose... I might never see you again.

nextDialogs.playerReply: I am not easily defeated, I will never think of 'retreat' or 'bribe' from the monster
nextDialogs.npcDialog: I believe you won't, but there are items that you might want to 'pick' up if you found any.

nextDialogs.playerReply: I can also 'drop' or 'consume' by item name right?
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Yes, you can, but be careful that your bag have a limited weight.

nextDialogs.playerReply: How do I check the weight then?
nextDialogs.npcDialog: You can check by 'bag' or look at yours 'stat'.

nextDialogs.playerReply: sounds cool, anything else?
nextDialogs.npcDialog: If you see any people like me, you can 'talk' to them, or 'trade' with aby merchants.

nextDialogs.playerReply: I can't remember all that you just said... sadly
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Don't worry, you can see what can you do by calling 'help'.

nextDialogs.playerReply: Oh thanks!  You are nice
nextDialogs.npcDialog: It is my pleasure to help you. Do you want some gold?.

nextDialogs.playerReply: No thanks, I want to earn the gold myself
Sure, thanks again!
Can I get something to eat during my adventure?
nextDialogs.npcDialog: Sure, you can have this lesser health potion.
